products.title: Banbury Canvas Curtain
products.description: Subtle and stylish, this curtain is ideal for enhancing a neutral scheme. The banbury canvas curtain features a clean geometric pattern of overlapping lines creating a dimensional woven effect. This design will suit a contemporary scheme or a more classic setting and features a full lining that is sure to give an elegant, quality look to the fabric. Product id: db-cur1172 fabric colour: canvas material: 78% polyester 14% cotton 8% linen lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - increase to er3 (high) by adding thermal lining light filtering: yes banbury canvas curtain in cream.
